  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313700/extras/233a2a03dd543494c39ce3d8c1ff358c.avif?t=1722152423\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>COVID Kawaii! is the cutest pandemic tower defense this side of the partition glass. Using the power of common sense and cleaning products, defend your personal space from the oncoming virus hoard. Can you go the social distance?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313700/extras/54b81750d10b180810d83d99b10a6313.webp?t=1722152423\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Follow the story of the COVID-19 pandemic.<br></li><li>Familiar yet challenging tower defense gameplay.<br></li><li>Collect and spend the elusive and rare TP rolls.<br></li><li>12 maps to defend with 3 single player difficulties.<br></li><li>Ranked PVP and Co-op for multiplayer fun.<br></li><li>Extensive Twitch integration, viewers can play along in the chat.<br></li><li>Multiple upgrades and cosmetics to unlock.<br></li><li>Doesn't require leaving your home.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313700/extras/233a2a03dd543494c39ce3d8c1ff358c.avif?t=1722152423\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br>COVID Kawaii! is the cutest pandemic tower defense this side of the partition glass. Using the power of common sense and cleaning products, defend your personal space from the oncoming virus hoard. Can you go the social distance?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1313700/extras/54b81750d10b180810d83d99b10a6313.webp?t=1722152423\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Follow the story of the COVID-19 pandemic.<br></li><li>Familiar yet challenging tower defense gameplay.<br></li><li>Collect and spend the elusive and rare TP rolls.<br></li><li>12 maps to defend with 3 single player difficulties.<br></li><li>Ranked PVP and Co-op for multiplayer fun.<br></li><li>Extensive Twitch integration, viewers can play along in the chat.<br></li><li>Multiple upgrades and cosmetics to unlock.<br></li><li>Doesn't require leaving your home.</li></ul>",
